- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper involves the use of machine learning techniques for language modeling and translation.
- cs.SD (Sound) is a possible category as the paper deals with speech translation, which involves sound processing.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves the use of various machine learning techniques for language modeling and translation.
- cs.SD (Signal Processing) is also a possible category as the paper involves the processing of speech signals.
